channel.title: (317) server status page problem! plz help! (317)
channel.description:
Ok so im really excited to get my server up.. but when i go to register it, it says its offline? WTF? Like look :
[code]!!Error:
The server BrainCold-Scape is offline, it must be online before you can register it here. [/code]
Like ffs? What am i doing wrong? The server "Run" Is on.. Everything is fine... PLZ HELP! IF YOU CAN!
